description.value:
Flow triggers when project is cancelled.

It will close all subtasks accordingly:

WHEN I Cancel a Project
THEN every non-completed task will be set to either Closed Incomplete or Closed Skipped. In Progress Tasks will be set Closed Incomplete. Non-Started Tasks will be set Closed Skipped. When all tasks are Closed Incomplete, Closed Skipped, or Completed the project will be set to Cancelled.

WHEN I Cancel a Project
